This House is just on a 5 mins to Tarneit Train station and 30 mins to Melbourne CBD.
An exceptional home perfectly suited to first home buyers, and investors. This gorgeous brand new dwelling offers a flexible layout presenting a fantastic opportunity for the astute buyer.

˗ Ducted heating and Split system cooling
˗ Enjoy outdoor living with Alfresco and Big Back yard

- Land size 579 sqm (approx.)

- All the hard work is done, just buy and move in.
Call Mandeep 0433 769 496 to arrange an inspection as this one won't last long.

Description:
Brand New Home in a Prime & Pristine Location
17 Lay Street Tarneit
GK Popli & Ray White Tarneit proudly present this absolutely beautiful brand new (under construction) house in the ever popular Emerald Park Estate.
This spectacular home embraces a modern feel with a succession of light filled living spaces. With superior fixtures and fittings all through and a great location, this home is the one you had been looking for all this long. The sustainable design of this home offers multiple living areas with a free flowing floor plan which is both practical and aesthetically appealing.
This fully upgraded home features 4 bedrooms. Master bedroom includes a spacious walk in robe and En-suite with an extended shower and toilet. Three more spacious bedrooms facilitated by spacious bathroom that includes extended shower and bath tub with separate toilet. This house encompasses living areas and dining areas, incorporating a superb kitchen fitted with upgraded 900mm appliances, stone bench tops, and Island bench with breakfast bar, ample work space and storage including walking pantry. With added features like ducted heating 2 car garage with remote control, contemporary neutral interiors, spacious laundry, and front landscaping, and alfresco sitting area.
Other inspired features include :-
-Master with a walk-in robe
-Remote Controlled double garage
-Fully Landscaped front yard
-Kitchen with walk in pantry
-High ceiling, down lights
-Grand alfresco sitting area
Fulfilling all the necessities of a convenient location and an active lifestyle, this compelling property investment opportunity is not to be missed.
Come and view this elevated and elegant family home that's certain to attract an assortment of potential buyers. Ray White Tarneit TEAM welcomes you and looks forward to servicing your real estate needs.
Please note that the photos are for illustration purposes only.
Call GK Popli on 0469 342 170 to arrange an inspection as this one won't last long.

Description:
East Facing Family Entertainer - Built in November 2016
10 Zambezi Street, Tarneit
First Home Owners Grant $10,000 applicable for eligible buyers!!
(Please check with State Revenue Office for eligibility and do your own due diligence)
Wonderfully presented and dressed with class throughout is this Metricon built gorgeous contemporary showstopper just perfect for those who want the space, yet won't compromise on quality.
10 Zambezi Street is a fabulous east facing single storey home with intelligent zoning, which sees a spacious floor plan layout play host to an elegant formal lounge, open plan living area adjacent to a stunning kitchen that delights with its abundant 20 mm stone bench space, walk in pantry and quality stainless steel appliances.
Slide open the glass door to unite the interior with fully decked outdoor entertainment area surrounded by expensive Zip track Blinds. Enjoy outdoor living area throughout the year! It's perfect for those weekends where you are entertaining friends and family or for the Christmas luncheons. It also offers spacious laundry room with ample linen storage.
10 Zambezi Street include 3 good sized fitted bedrooms, spacious master bedroom with stone bench-top vanity en-suite, walk in robe and the remaining 2 bedrooms with mirror built in robes serviced by a central bathroom.
Inspired features are everywhere:
- Ducted Heating & Evaporative Cooling - Making you feel comfortable all around the year
- 2.55m High Ceilings
- Wishper Blinds to windows:Combining all the practical benefits and advantages of curtains, shades and blinds into one highly intelligent window covering
- Plantation Shutters to windows in Bathrooms
- Double glazed glass on all windows
- Crimsafe security doors to entrance, laundry & outdoor living area
- Down-lights all throughout the house
- Laminate timber flooring in the living areas & carpets in bedrooms
- Shower Niche in ensuite as well as main bathroom
- 20 mm kitchen stone bench-top, 900 mm gas cook top & dishwasher
- Low maintenance front and backyard with raised color-bond fencing for privacy
- Remote control double lock up garage and much more
This family home is situated in the popular The Grove Estate, close to all family essentials like as follows:
- Approx 2.4 kms to Davis Creek Primary School
- Approx 2.4 kms to Tarneit West Shopping Centre
- Approx 2 kms to Riverdale Village Shopping Centre
- Bus stop to Tarneit train station at 10 minutes walk
- Walking Distance to Werribee River walk and bicycle trails
Ray White Tarneit welcomes you and looks forward to meet you at the open homes.
Call Mike on 0430 126 491 today to set an appointment for private inspection!!
(PHOTO ID REQUIRED AT OPEN FOR INSPECTION)

Description:
Emerald Park Estate
Emerald Park in central Tarneit gives you your brand new dream home with all the convenience of the Town Centre at your back door.
Yet, you can be in the Melbourne CBD by car or train in less than half an hour. Just 1100 residential blocks forming a unique community close to Tarneit train station with nearby primary, secondary schools and shopping centers plus a huge Indoor/outdoor recreation facility offering football, netball, tennis, and cricket. Right now is your chance to invest in a new lifestyle with a home that offers so much more. And it's all brand new.
Also, a childcare center and medical clinic are opening soon.

Build your dream home sooner on this titled lot at Riverwalk.

Description:
Lot 2713 Gorkha Way PREMIUM - THE PROMENADE Collection 4
Create an enviable lifestyle at The Promenade, the gateway to the exceptional Riverwalk Premium within the established Riverwalk community in dynamic Werribee. Surround yourself with natural beauty in this exclusive parkside setting where more than 100,000 sqm of lush Riverfront parkland is just five minutes walk away.
The Promenades impressive entry features a wide tree-lined boulevard delivering a unique opportunity to nestle your dream home amongst mature trees and street landscaping. Enjoy an active lifestyle with the utmost convenience with Lollipop Creek and the Village Park within easy walking distance. A shared path will connect you to the Federation Trail that meanders beside the Werribee River for a scenic journey into the heart of Werribee. Take advantage of regular bus services to the suburbs flourishing amenity from a bus stop right on your doorstep. A premium parkside lifestyle by the river awaits at The Promenade.
A project by Development Victoria. Visit myriverwalk.com.au

Low Maintenance Living Close to everything
OKAS Property Group & Vish Safi proud to present this immaculate unit in the heart of Deer Park
The home boasts modern, stylish and low maintenance living all within minutes of Ballarat road Shopping Strip, parks, transportation and schools. Comprising of a large master bedroom with walk in robe and en-suite, the other two spacious bedrooms both come BIR's. Upon entering the home is the large living/dining area all flowing to the state-of-the-art modern kitchen with stainless steel appliances. The back yard is elegantly presented with a pergola and space to sit and relax with your family and friends
Other features include gas ducted heating, evaporative cooking, high ceilings, tiles in wet area and carpet in bed rooms and single car remote garage with extra shelving and internal access.
You would not want to delay seeing this opportunity

Description:
Perfect solution for large, busy families
This light-filled Simonds home offers you the opportunity to move straight in and embrace the convenience of Elements estate lifestyle without having to lift a finger! With four bedrooms, two livings, two-bathrooms, a study and a fully functional butler's pantry with its own cook-top, rangehood and dishwasher it is sure to impress the fussiest of buyers. There is a range of luxurious upgrades throughout this home and 18 solar panels backed up with a 6kw Fronius inverter.
The well planned, flowing layout is ideal for a family. Situated only 5 minutes to Tarneit train station, opposite to upcoming bike track/parkland and minutes to local shopping centres, this home has all your needs covered in style.
Kitchen - At the heart of this home is a lovingly designed kitchen with 40mm stone benchtops, pendant lights over breakfast bench, overhead cupboards, 900mm gas cooktop, oven & rangehood, large butler's pantry with another 4 stove burner & rangehood, SS dishwasher and a beautiful mother of pearl tile splashback.
Living Area - Open plan adjoining living, dining & kitchen, timber flooring throughout, LED downlights, zoned ducted heating, evaporative cooling & stunning pendant lights over living zone, roller blinds, glass sliding doors open from living to outdoor alfresco.
Second living- Carpeted, LED down lights, well-lit through large window that are double glazed with crimsafe saving energy and adding another layer of security, roller blinds & privately located at the front of home with double doors entrance. This space can also be used as a theater room, it is set up with all the essential electrical points and a sound reducing thermal insulation in the walls.
Master bedroom- Carpeted, walk in robe and ensuite with double vanity and extended bench space & storage, large shower head with niche, personal toilet. This bedroom also has a nook that is specifically designed to get an access to the kids bedroom as well as glass sliding doors opening to backyard alfresco with double block out roller blinds.
Additional three bedrooms- carpeted, roller blinds, ducted heating & cooling, LED down lights, floor to ceiling sliding mirrored built in robes.
Main bathroom- Floor to ceiling tiles, semi frame less shower with niche, long bath, single vanity and separate toilet.
Outdoor- Undercover Tiled alfresco & lights, low maintenance backyard with artificial turf, mounted foldable clothesline arranged on the side house wall & sensor light.
Additional- Simonds build approximately 27 sq on 461 m2, Creek facing, multi Zoned ducted heating & evaporative cooling throughout for year round comfort, 2.74 meter ceiling height (approx), backyard alfresco access from living & master bedroom, laundry with linen cupboard, broom cupboard & outdoor access, , double lock up garage with backyard and internal access with entry night lock, exposed aggregate concrete driveway, 18 solar panels backed up with a 6kw Fronius inverter.
Security features- Camera surveillance front and back, double glazed windows with Crimsafe security screens, double door front entrance with entry night lock.
If you've been searching for a stylish, quality built modern home then look no further. There is nothing to be done here, just move in and enjoy the lifestyle this location offers.

Description:
Lifestyle, Location and a 1/4 acre!
Set amongst quality homes in the desirable tree lined Derrimut Heath Estate, this beautiful owner built character filled home is on the market for the very first time. Quality, attention to detail meets a flexible family floor plan with dual living zones. The formal lounge and dining room feature ceiling roses, arches and period lighting. Comprising four generous fitted bedrooms - Master bedroom with WIR and ensuite and three additional fitted bedrooms serviced by a period charm bathroom with deep soaking tub. Gorgeous oak kitchen with American redwood stain is the central focal hub and provides an open plan feel between the meals area and expansive family room. The well maintained rear garden with several fruit and mature trees enjoys a northerly aspect. A large timber lined and stained pergola with built in surround sound audio system is ready for entertaining family and friends. Wide side access and a second large pergola offers protection for a vehicle, boat, trailer, caravan etc.
A host of extras include: high ceilings, extensive oak flooring, decorative Victorian cornices, luxury vinyl floor planks, ducted gas heating, evaporative cooling and near new Daikin Split system. Quality classic clinker bricks, large work shed, larger than normal double garage with adjoining storage room/workshop, timber lined verandas and large laundry with ample storage.
Don't miss out on this rare gem - inspection is a must!

Description:
OFF MARKET SOLD
Reliance Real Estate proudly presents 18 Trentbridge Road, Tarneit, This home 26 sqs built and located in the ever popular 'New Gate Estate' and is conveniently located near primary schools, Good News Lutheran school & ICOM, close to so many amenities like Wyndham Village shopping Centre, Tarneit West Shopping Centre, Medical centers, Parklands, Child care and much more.
Embrace the executive lifestyle this home brings - family comfort & convenience with a east facing position, this home strikes a balance between light and space welcoming you with landscaped front & back with following features:
A royal master bedroom offers an ultimate private indulgence of luxury, en-suite comprising of extended shower with specious walk in robes
Additional three bedrooms with built in robes
Elegant light filled open plan kitchen with stone bench top, designer lights, glass splash back, 900mm stainless steel appliances with specious walk in butler's pantry
Wide front entrance will take you to an open plan contemporary style from where you will look out to the family living and dining extending to beautifully covered pergola allowing the versatility to entertain the guests when required.
Good size formal lounge/Theatre room to welcome and entertain guests
Decent size of laundry with storage space
Internal intercom with Alarm system
Upgraded blinds through out the home
Aggregated driveway and concrete path all around house
Ducted heating & cooling making you feel comfortable all around the year
Double car garage with rear and internal access for added convenience
Separate specious Powder room
LED down lights throughout the home
Stunning timber floorboards running all through the House
A phenomenal opportunity with loads of extras. Highly recommended for buyers who appreciate finer things, style, location and lifestyle.
Please feel free to contact Kanan Patel on 0433 410 105 or Prince Dhir on 0411 552 685 for any query related to this property!!!

Description:
Luxurious Ex Display in the heart of Truganina ''Westbrook Estate''
Ray White Truganina presents this perfectly positioned Ex display home by ''Dennis family Homes'' located in a Premium estate "Westbrook" in Truganina. Layered in light-filled luxury and sensationally steeped in elegant style, this stunning 4 bedroom family home captivates with contemporary indoor/outdoor flow over two flawless levels.
This family home is an outstanding opportunity to simply move into a dream home you have been looking for. This first class residence with impeccable attention to detail simply oozes with quality from every angle whilst catering above and beyond for your family's needs.
The impressive upper level contains a family retreat, accompanied by exquisite style four bedrooms and two bathrooms. Master bedroom includes a large balcony, lavish en suite with double vanity, oversized shower and a huge walk-in-robe. All the remaining three bedrooms include walk in robe as well
Adjoining to the living and dining areas, the kitchen is a dream come true with top quality appliances by technika including top quality ovens, range hood, 900mm gas cooktop, stone bench tops, dishwasher and generous storage including walk in pantry.
Features Include:
*Boasting 4 spacious bedrooms and all with walk in robes.
*Four living areas
*Featured walls
*Fly screens
*Light filled hostess kitchen featuring stone bench tops, high end 900mm appliances, dishwasher, walk in pantry and pended lights
*Security alarm
*Evaporative cooling
*Solar water
*Ducted heating
*Decked alfresco and Featured roof
*Outdoor BBQ space with gas point
*2 car remote garage with internal access
*Privacy Screens
Just 24 kilometres from Melbourne's CBD; Westbrook Estate brings you close to all the best amenities, including schools, parks, shops, childcares, transport and easy access to freeways. Many schooling opportunities which include, Westbourne Grammar, St Clares Catholic Primary School and conveniently walking distance to Truganina P-9 school. The estate is couple of minutes drive to Tarneit Station and upcoming Truganina Station
Don't miss the opportunity to call this elegant family home yours that's certain to attract all buyers looking for their dream home.
Call Roy on 0432 348 652 or Mark on 0425 400 600 to arrange an inspection as this one won't last long

Description:
CLOSE TO EVERYTHING - POTENIAL SUB DIVISION - STCA
Attention investors, developers and home buyers!!! This priceless gem is perfectly suited to buyers who are looking for a home to move into, investment property to add to their portfolio or potential sub-division (STCA) - the opportunities are endless!
Built on 788 sqm corner block, this home has plenty to offer complete with Spacious living area, three good sized bedrooms, with a light and bright central bathroom. The kitchen includes gas cook top, oven and abundance of cupboard space all overlooking the open plan dining area with separate toilet. .
Its positioned in a superb location - walking distance to Schools, Central Werribee, cafes, Restaurants and 500m from Werribee Train Station.
Set on 788sqm land, there is a garage at the rear of the property making an ideal for any buyer who needs extra storage for a caravan, boat, cars, trailers or machinery.
This property is perfect for any developer who is looking for a property in a prime location, you can leave the original home and build a 2nd dwelling at the rear or can accommodate 4 new townhouses (STCA)
Features & Benefits:
Approx. 788sqm land - potential sub-division (STCA)

Garage

500m to Werribee CBD
